Careers with impact.
Diamond Offshore Drilling is a recognized leader in deepwater drilling and provides contract drilling services to the energy industry worldwide. Being an industry leader means holding a steadfast commitment to the attainment of goals in critical areas of operational excellence and safety.Just as significant is the commitment we make to our people.

