Careers Overview
 Working at Diamond Offshore




Safety is a Core Value 


A relentless commitment to safety is at the core of our training and operations.
 Safety Programs



We Value our People


We invest in our people by providing comprehensive benefits and training.
 Total Career Benefits




Premier industry training and career development opportunities for all of our team members enable them to pursue a career path that best provides for their future and meets the changing needs of our customers.
We recognize that our ability to deliver success to our customers and value to our shareholders is contingent on the skills and dedication of the 2,800 men and women of Diamond Offshore. We offer rewarding career opportunities, amazing salary and benefits packages and training that is second-to-none. We pride ourselves in the retention of our people. Above all, our relentless obsession with safety is at the core of our training and operations.
Diamond Offshore is an equal opportunity employer.


Training Facility


Our high-tech training facility, The Ocean Technology Center, houses our industry-leading priority training programs and simulations.
