Diamond Offshore is a leader in offshore drilling, providing contract drilling services to the energy industry around the globe with a total fleet of 24 offshore drilling rigs, consisting of 19 semisubmersibles, four dynamically positioned drillships, and one jack-up.
The Ocean BlackHawk was delivered in mid-2014, and sister rigs, the Ocean BlackHornet, Ocean BlackRhino, were delivered at the end of 2014; the fourth newbuild drillship, the Ocean BlackLion, was delivered in the second quarter of 2015. We have also constructed two deepwater semisubmersible rigs, named Ocean Apex and Ocean Onyx, that were delivered in 2014. The Ocean GreatWhite, our ultra-deepwater harsh environment semisubmersible, was recently delivered and is currently in its contract term.
Individual Rig Details are below, but you may also download the specification sheets for the entire fleet. Download All Spec Sheets PDF (5.9MB)




Video: The Ocean Endeavor Completes a Well-Planned, Perfectly Executed Journey





